### ========================================
### 28 - Records Sharing & Patient Consent
### Share, Resolve, Export, Consent Management
### ========================================

### ----------------------------------------
### RECORD SHARING
### ----------------------------------------

### Share patient records (explicit source → target)
POST {{baseUrl}}/records/share
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "{{patientId}}",
  "fromHospitalId": "{{hospitalId}}",
  "toHospitalId": "{{hospitalId2}}"
}

### Smart resolve: auto-pick consent path (SAME_HOSPITAL → INTRA_ORG → CROSS_ORG)
GET {{baseUrl}}/records/resolve?patientId={{patientId}}&requestingHospitalId={{hospitalId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Export patient record as PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/records/export?patientId={{patientId}}&fromHospitalId={{hospitalId}}&toHospitalId={{hospitalId2}}&format=pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/pdf

### Export patient record as CSV
POST {{baseUrl}}/records/export?patientId={{patientId}}&fromHospitalId={{hospitalId}}&toHospitalId={{hospitalId2}}&format=csv
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: text/csv

### ----------------------------------------
### PATIENT CONSENT
### ----------------------------------------

### Grant consent (with optional scope filtering)
POST {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents/grant
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "patientId": "{{patientId}}",
  "fromHospitalId": "{{hospitalId}}",
  "toHospitalId": "{{hospitalId2}}",
  "purpose": "Specialist referral",
  "consentExpiration": "2027-02-14T00:00:00",
  "consentType": "TREATMENT",
  "scope": "ENCOUNTERS,LAB_RESULTS,PRESCRIPTIONS"
}

### Revoke consent
POST {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents/revoke?patientId={{patientId}}&fromHospitalId={{hospitalId}}&toHospitalId={{hospitalId2}}
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

### List all consents (paginated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{superAdminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get consents by patient
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents/patient/{{patientId}}?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get consents from hospital
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents/from-hospital/{{hospitalId}}?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get consents to hospital
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents/to-hospital/{{hospitalId2}}?page=0&size=20
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Check if consent is active
GET {{baseUrl}}/patient-consents/active?patientId={{patientId}}&fromHospitalId={{hospitalId}}&toHospitalId={{hospitalId2}}
Authorization: Bearer {{doctorToken}}
Accept: application/json
